Narrative:
Sun bidding goodbye
Giving us all heat and dire 
Like ripe mangoes 
Stays still high 
Moments 
We meet in sometime 
Gleefully 
To return 
With hopeful tomorrows 
To say some goodbyes 
Forever in time
Title: Goodbyes
